  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered project planning with Gemini 3 Pro generating dependency-aware task graphs",
    "Isolated E2B sandbox execution with Gemini CLI in YOLO mode",
    "Automatic GitHub PR creation for every completed task",
    "Real-time execution log streaming via Upstash Realtime pub/sub",
    "Human-in-the-loop review workflow: approve, request changes, or merge in-platform",
    "Task state machine progressing from PENDING → RUNNING → REVIEW → DONE",
    "Preview agent turning rough ideas into structured project metadata",
    "Security: secrets injected via env vars and redacted from all logs"
